descript.abstract: Populated Places (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World Gazetteer data set. The geographic and attribute data of World Gazetteer are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features (Populated places) are symbolized as a single symbol and labeled based on the NAME attribute.
descript.purpose: Populated Places (layer) provides a common and useful display of World Gazetteer for a better understanding of the data set contents. Add this layer to a map to display useful information about the data set and that integrates well with other data set layers.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
